@Reqrefusion Why would a grant be needed?

@Reqrefusion thank you for the kind words. There is one more installment remaining, and I'm planning to request that once I have extracted the stated operations out of `SketchObject` into separate files.

My plan has been that this would be the last of the paid refactors, and then, since the largest and most complex parts would be done, further refactorings be done as other bugfixes and features are done (of course ideally as separate commits), not just by me but also other developers. Ideally, I would like to continue with some more "interesting" parts of development as well, like the new curves I proposed.

Unfortunately, I haven't been able to give the right amount (and quality) of time to any of the ongoing grants, for various reasons. Additionally, there are already bugs discovered in the currently merged refactors. So I'd hold off on any further grant requests till all that is sorted. I will have slightly more time over the next two months, so hopefully there's more progress.

